def has_coffee_filter_on_cup(cup:item):
    # Function to check if there is a coffee filter on a specified cup
    symbol has_coffee_filter=exists filter: item : is_coffee_filter(filter) and on(filter, cup)
    return has_coffee_filter

behavior place_coffee_maker_on_counter(coffee_maker:item, kitchen_counter:item):
    body:
        achieve on(coffee_maker, kitchen_counter)

behavior add_water_to_coffee_maker(coffee_maker:item, faucet:item):
    body:
        achieve has_water(coffee_maker)

behavior brew_coffee(coffee_maker:item):
    body:
        achieve is_on(coffee_maker)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind coffee_maker: item where:
            is_coffe_maker(coffee_maker)
        bind kitchen_counter: item where:
            is_kitchen_counter(kitchen_counter)
        place_coffee_maker_on_counter(coffee_maker, kitchen_counter)

        if exists cup: item : is_cup(cup) and has_coffee_filter_on_cup(cup):
            bind cup: item where:
                is_cup(cup) and has_coffee_filter_on_cup(cup)
            achieve on(cup, kitchen_counter)
        else:
            foreach cup: item:
                if is_cup(cup) and not visited(cup):
                    observe(cup,"Check is there any coffee filter on the cup")

        if exists faucet: item : is_faucet(faucet) and close(faucet, coffee_maker):
            bind faucet: item where:
                is_faucet(faucet) and close(faucet, coffee_maker)
            add_water_to_coffee_maker(coffee_maker, faucet)
        else:
            foreach faucet: item:
                if is_faucet(faucet) and not visited(faucet):
                    observe(faucet,"Check if faucet is close to the coffee maker")

        brew_coffee(coffee_maker)

def has_milk_and_sugar(kitchen_counter:item):
    # Check if milk and sugar are on the specified kitchen counter
    symbol has_milk_and_sugar = exists o: item : (is_milk(o) or is_food_sugar(o)) and on(o, kitchen_
counter)
    return has_milk_and_sugar

behavior add_milk_and_sugar_to_coffee(cup:item, milk:item, sugar:item, kitchen_counter:item):
    body:
        # Move milk and sugar onto the same surface as the coffee cup
        achieve close(cup, kitchen_counter) 
        achieve_once inhand(milk)
        achieve on(milk, cup)
        achieve_once inhand(sugar)
        achieve on(sugar, cup)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind coffe_maker: item where:
            is_coffe_maker(coffe_maker)

        bind cup: item where:
            is_cup(cup) and close(cup, coffe_maker)

        bind kitchen_counter: item where:
            is_kitchen_counter(kitchen_counter)

        if has_milk_and_sugar(kitchen_counter):
            # If milk and sugar are already present on the kitchen counter, proceed to add them to t
he coffee
            bind milk: item where:
                is_milk(milk) and on(milk, kitchen_counter)
            bind sugar: item where:
                is_food_sugar(sugar) and on(sugar, kitchen_counter)
            add_milk_and_sugar_to_coffee(cup, milk, sugar, kitchen_counter)
        else:
            # If not, use observation to find milk and sugar
            observe(kitchen_counter, "Check is there any milk and sugar on the kitchen counter")

def has_milk_sugar_on_kitchen_counter(counter:item):
    # Function to check if there is milk or sugar on the kitchen counter
    symbol has_milk_sugar=exists o: item : (is_milk(o) or is_food_sugar(o)) and on(o, counter)
    return has_milk_sugar

behavior add_to_coffee(milk:item, sugar:item, coffee:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(milk, coffee)
        achieve inside(sugar, coffee)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind coffee: item where:
            is_cup(coffee) and is_dining_room(coffee)
        # Select coffee cup inside dining room

        bind kitchen_counter: item where:
            is_kitchen_counter(kitchen_counter)
        # Select a kitchen counter

        if has_milk_sugar_on_kitchen_counter(kitchen_counter):
            bind milk: item where:
                is_milk(milk) and on(milk, kitchen_counter)
            bind sugar: item where:
                is_food_sugar(sugar) and on(sugar, kitchen_counter)
            add_to_coffee(milk, sugar, coffee)
        else:
            observe(kitchen_counter, "Is there any milk or sugar on the counter")

    # Function to check if there is milk or sugar on the kitchen counter
    symbol has_milk_or_sugar = exists o: item : (is_milk(o) or is_food_sugar(o)) and on(o, kitchen_c
ounter)
    return has_milk_or_sugar

behavior add_milk_and_sugar(cup: item, milk: item, sugar: item):
    body:
        achieve inside(milk, cup) # Pour milk into the cup
        achieve inside(sugar, cup) # Pour sugar into the cup

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind kitchen_counter: item where:
            is_kitchen_counter(kitchen_counter)
        # Select a kitchen counter

        if has_milk_or_sugar(kitchen_counter):
            bind milk: item where:
                is_milk(milk) and on(milk, kitchen_counter)
            # Select milk on the kitchen counter

            bind sugar: item where:
                is_food_sugar(sugar) and on(sugar, kitchen_counter)
            # Select sugar on the kitchen counter

            bind coffee_cup: item where:
                is_cup(coffee_cup) and drinkable(coffee_cup)
            # Select the cup of brewed coffee

            add_milk_and_sugar(coffee_cup, milk, sugar)
            # Add milk and sugar to the brewed coffee

def has_coffee_and_milk(cup:item):
    symbol has_coffee=exists o: item : (is_food_sugar(o) or is_milk(o)) and inside(o, cup)
    return has_coffee

behavior add_milk_and_sugar(cup:item, milk:item, sugar:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(milk, cup)
        achieve inside(sugar, cup)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind coffee_cup: item where:
            is_cup(coffee_cup) and visited(coffee_cup)
        
        if not has_coffee_and_milk(coffee_cup):
            bind milk: item where:
                is_milk(milk) and close(milk, coffee_cup)
            bind sugar: item where:
                is_food_sugar(sugar) and close(sugar, coffee_cup)
            add_milk_and_sugar(coffee_cup, milk, sugar)
